# TypeScript in this repo

- Bots use `tsc` → `dist/`; run via `yarn workspace <name> start` or root `start:*` scripts after build.
- Use the workspace dependency `@bsky-bots/common` instead of duplicating shared ATProto or helper logic.
- Follow existing ESLint and Prettier setup (root `eslint.config` / `lint-staged`); fix lint on touched files.
- Keep Node/types aligned with each package’s `devDependencies` (`@types/node`, `typescript`).
